/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn98069867/1920-12-17/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "rights": ["<p>The Library of Congress believes that the newspapers in Chronicling America are in the public domain or have no known copyright restrictions.  Newspapers published in the United States more than 95 years ago are in the public domain in their entirety. Any newspapers in Chronicling America that were published less than 95 years ago are also believed to be in the public domain, but may contain some copyrighted third party materials. Researchers using newspapers published less than 95 years ago should be alert for modern content (for example, registered and renewed for copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.331948, "shard": "06", "shelf_id": "sn98069867, 1920-12-17, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/tu", "subject": ["memphis", "shelby", "shelby county (tenn.)", "newspapers", "united states", "memphis (tenn.)", "shelby county", "tennessee"], "subject_headings": ["Memphis (Tenn.)--Newspapers", "Shelby County (Tenn.)--Newspapers", "Tennessee--Memphis", "Tennessee--Shelby County", "United States--Tennessee--Shelby--Memphis"], "subjects": [{"memphis": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:memphis&fo=json"}, {"memphis (tenn.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:memphis+%28tenn.%29&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"shelby": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:shelby&fo=json"}, {"shelby county": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:shelby+county&fo=json"}, {"shelby county (tenn.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:shelby+county+%28tenn.%29&fo=json"}, {"tennessee": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:tennessee&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2022-10-27T19:27:13.155Z", "title": "The news scimitar (Memphis, Tenn.), December 17, 1920, (FOURTH EDITION)", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn98069867/1920-12-17/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn98069867/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn98069867"], "batch": ["tu_carla_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1907", "description": ["Daily (except Sun.), May 3-Nov. 15, 1926 Vol. 28, no. 336 (Dec. 2, 1907)-v. 46, no. 291 (Nov. 15, 1926). \"Memphis\" appears in masthead ornament Apr. 1, 1921-Nov. 15, 1926. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Merged with: Memphis press, to form: Memphis press-scimitar. Memphis press (DLC)sn 00063946 Memphis press-scimitar (DLC)sn 86071112"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:00.643Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "catalog-split-06", "catalog", "ndnp/newspapers", "main-catalog-split-06", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn98069867/", "image_url": [], "index": 3, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [35.1433781, -90.0521356], "location": ["memphis", "shelby", "united states", "shelby county", "tennessee"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-90.0521356, 35.1433781], "number": ["sn86071112", "670", "tennessee state libr & arch", "microfilm master", "2473-3199", "sn98069867", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn98069867/1918-10-22/ed-1/", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2025-06-25t14:26:06", "sn88061115", "univ of memphis", "39898320", "sn00063946", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn98069867/1920-12-31/ed-1/", "2020-10-18t21:43:43.668562", "online resource", "1", "microfilm service copy"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Sunday illustrated news scimitar", "Memphis news scimitar", "Sunday issues for Sept. 6, 1925-Apr. 25, 1926 have title: Sunday illustrated news scimitar"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "chronicling america", "catalog", "the news scimitar (memphis, tenn.) 1907-1926", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 75.86693, "shelf_id": "Newspaper", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "catalog", "usnd"], "subject": ["memphis", "shelby", "shelby county (tenn.)", "newspapers", "united states", "memphis (tenn.)", "shelby county", "tennessee"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:39:13.128Z", "title": "The news scimitar.", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn98069867/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2021220289/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1847", "dates": ["[1847 TO 1886]"], "description": ["Daily (except Monday), Apr. 7, 1874-Jan. 27, 1886 Print began July 1847. Print ceased with v. 46, no. 23 (Jan. 27, 1886). Published irregularly June 6, 1862-Nov. 5, 1865 at Hernando, Grenada, Jackson, and Vicksburg, Miss.; Atlanta, Griffin, and Macon, Ga.; Montgomery and Selma, Ala. Sun. & Mon. editions published on front/back same sheet <1864>. Suspended: July 5-14, 1848; Dec. 1-12, 1862; & Apr. 11-17, 1864. Also issued in print. Mode of access: World Wide Web. Vol. VII, No. 246 (January 1, 1857); title from caption (Chronicling America's website, viewed Apr. 19, 2021). Vol. XLVI, No. 23 (January 27, 1886) (Chronicling America's website, viewed Apr. 19, 2021). Memphis appeal"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:17.248Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2021220289/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["vicksburg", "fulton", "united states", "de soto", "grenada", "dallas", "memphis", "hinds", "selma", "georgia", "fulton county", "shelby county", "warren", "atlanta", "macon", "mississippi", "spalding", "bibb", "shelby", "montgomery", "jackson", "hernando", "tennessee", "griffin", "alabama"], "number": ["online resource", "778032516", "2021220289", "2768-0355", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Sunday issues for <June 7, 1868>-Oct. 17, 1869 have title: Sunday appeal", "Sunday issues for Oct. 24, 1869-Apr. 5, 1874 have title: Memphis Sunday appeal", "Issues for June 20-21, 1882, Jan. 2-Apr. 8, 1877 & July 15-31, 1885 have title: Daily Memphis appeal", "Colophon title: Daily appeal", "Memphis appeal"], "partof": ["memphis daily appeal (memphis, tenn.) 1847-1886 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 66.62525, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["vicksburg", "united states", "fulton", "de soto", "grenada", "dallas", "memphis", "hinds", "selma", "georgia", "newspapers", "fulton county", "memphis (tenn.)", "shelby county", "fulton county (ga.)", "atlanta", "warren", "macon", "mississippi", "spalding", "bibb", "atlanta (ga.)", "shelby", "montgomery", "shelby county (tenn.)", "jackson", "hernando", "tennessee", "griffin", "alabama"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:02:05.412Z", "title": "Memphis daily appeal", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2021220289/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2019271249/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1910", "dates": ["[1910 TO 1920]"], "description": ["Weekly, -1920 Began with volume XV, no. 1 (January 8, 1910); ceased in October 1920. \"A farm and home weekly for the states of Mississippi, Alabama, Louisiana, Arkansas, and Tennessee\" 1910- ; \"A farm and home weekly for Alabama, Mississippi, Tennessee and Arkansas\"--1920. Published at Birmingham, Ala. and Memphis, Tenn., -1920. Called \"Central ed.\"--1920. Description based on: Volume XV, No. 1 (January 8, 1910); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed September 17, 2019). Latest issue consulted: Vol. XXVIII, No. 13 (March 29, 1913) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed September 17, 2019). Progressive farmer (Birmingham, Ala. : 1920)"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:49.584Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2019271249/", "image_url": [], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["memphis", "shelby", "mississippi", "oktibbeha", "jefferson", "birmingham", "united states", "shelby county", "southern states", "jefferson county", "tennessee", "starkville", "alabama"], "number": ["online resource", "2019271249", "2019271168", "1119724206", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2688-9927"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Progressive farmer", "Southern farm gazette"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the progressive farmer and southern farm gazette (starkville, miss.) 1910-1920 [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 66.62525, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["jefferson", "united states", "southern states", "starkville (miss.)", "memphis", "newspapers", "memphis (tenn.)", "shelby county", "birmingham (ala.)", "mississippi", "oktibbeha", "birmingham", "starkville", "shelby", "jefferson county (ala.)", "shelby county (tenn.)", "agriculture", "jefferson county", "tennessee", "alabama"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:58:47.437Z", "title": "The progressive farmer and southern farm gazette", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2019271249/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2014218281/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1886", "dates": ["[1886 TO 1890]"], "description": ["Daily, Apr. 18, 1887-Nov. 8, 1890 Began with vol. XLVI, no. 24 (January 28, 1886); ceased November 8, 1890. Merged with: Memphis avalanche (Memphis, Tenn. : Daily : 1885), to form: Appeal-avalanche. Description based on: Vol. XLVI, no. 24 (January 28, 1886); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed April 23, 2014). Latest issue consulted: Vol. XLIX, no. 155 (June 30, 1889) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed April 23, 2014). Memphis avalanche (Memphis, Tenn. : Daily : 1885 : Online) Appeal-avalanche (Online)"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:25.703Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2014218281/", "image_url": [], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["memphis", "shelby", "united states", "shelby county", "tennessee"], "number": ["online resource", "877959090", "2014218281", "2372-5478", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Memphis daily appeal"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "the memphis appeal (memphis, tenn.) 1886-1890 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 66.62525, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["memphis", "shelby", "shelby county (tenn.)", "newspapers", "united states", "memphis (tenn.)", "shelby county", "tennessee"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:50:11.310Z", "title": "The Memphis appeal"